snippet.title: Cube Escape: The Cave | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
An old man is about to enter a mysterious Cave. A familiar guest needs your help before you descend deeper and deeper into Rusty Lake.

Download now for iOS (Iphone and Ipad):
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1209468207
Download on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeTheCave
Or play on web:
http://www.rustylake.com/room-escape-games/cube-escape-the-cave.html

Play more Cube Escape games at RustyLake.com

The Cave is the ninth episode of the Cube Escape series and is a continuation of the Rusty Lake story. We will unfold Rusty Lake mysteries one step at a time. So check RustyLake.com every day for new content.

Like and follow:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rustylakecom
Twitter: https://twitter.com/rustylakecom
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rustylakecom/
And subscribe to our mailing list: http://eepurl.com/bhphw1

Special thanks to:
Victor Butzelaar: http://www.victorbutzelaar.com/ (Soundtrack)
Bob Rafferty: http://www.bobrafferty.co.uk/ (Voice & Trailer)
